2026-03-18 phase-native-cleanup:
- Removed native-backend fallback paths from `core.project`, `core.doc.search`, `core.commands.findreplace`, `findfile`, `projectsearch`, `projectreplace`, `treeview`, `lsp.client`, and large parts of `lsp.server-manager`.
